well how do i Check the bounds that it checks for sending the wildy level interface

Posting on here for a tutorial is asking us to spoon feed you, which is not what this economy is about. It’s about further understand JAVA and being able to accomplish more than just renaming the server and releasing as your own. The search button up there at the top right does wonders, if you use it correctly. It’s like… The ultimate RSPS guide, because you can find just about anything.
[/quote]

How is spoonfeeding related to economy?[/quote]

Here is how spoon feeding is related to economy:
Spoon feeding = Person + Person + Valuable Information
Valuable Information = Valuables + Information
Valuables = Money
Money + People = Economy
Therefore
Spoon Feeding = Economy
